      About this item

      • Wireless remote control: Suitable for a variety of electrical devices; Easily control with an on-off switch; Ideal for almost all appliances, including lamps, electric coffee pot, fans, heaters, sound systems, holiday decorations, and charging devices
      • Strong RF Signal-100 FT Range: This mini wireless remote control outlet works well even through doors, walls, and windows, available for indoor, without interfering with other appliances; The line of sight is up to 100 feet
      • Space Saving: This compact designed remote control plug outlet only takes up 1 wall socket; Help you use as many outlets as possible in a limited space
      • Programmable and Expandable: Through custom programming, one remote control can control all outlets and the same remote outlet can be controlled by several remote control
      • Made For Everyone: This indoor remote control outlet is suitable for the elderly or the mobility impaired; After the power cut, the socket remains closed to save energy

      Product Description


      We strive to build on better living. We’re innovators, passionate about life and the things that make it better. When you partner with Syantek, you partner with the future.

      • Package Includes:
      • ETL and FCC certified Remote Control Electrical Outlet x 3
      • Remote Control x 1
      • 12 V(23 A) Battery x 1

      SYANTEK COMPACT SIZE REMOTE CONTROL OUTLETS

      Convenient your life

      Syantek remote control outlet with wireless for household appliances is suitable for outdoor and indoor use, meeting all your need; Apply to bedroom, bathroom, kitchen, living room and hotel, etc.

      Simply plug and play. Just press one button to control devices anywhere.

      • Specifications:
      • Working voltage for socket: 120 V~/60 Hz
      • Max Power Rating: 10A/1200W
      • Transmission frequency: 433.92 MHz
      • Remote Control Distance: 100 Feet /30 Meter(Free Area)
      • Remote Battery: DC 12 V/23 A

      Compact Design

      This mini remote control receptacle is designed for space-saving. Only occupying 1 wall socket, won’t affect the use of other plugs.

      Freely remote control:100 FT/ 30 M range

      Strong RF signal works well even through doors, walls, and windows up to 100 feet / 30 meters range. Available for indoor and outdoor use. Just control appliances with fingertips to make remote control come true.

      Made for Everyone

      Designed to provide convenience for everyone, including the elderly, pregnant women, and the physically challenged.

      How customer reviews and ratings work

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
